EXECUTIVE UNIFORM RENTAL, INC., etc. and Laundramation Corp., etc., Petitioners, v. SANITARY LINEN SERVICE CO. OF FLORIDA, etc., et al., Respondents. No. 42767. Supreme Court of Florida. Nov. 17, 1972. ROBERTS, C. J., and CARLTON, ADKINS and BOYD, JJ., concur. ERVIN, J., dissents.

Rehearing Denied Jan. 12, 1973.
